&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p style="text-align:center; line-height:38px; color:#0083ab; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; ">CERTIFICATE OF AUTHENTICITY (COA)<br>100% MONEY BACK LIFETIME GUARANTEE</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p style="text-align:center; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; font-family: ''Questrial'', Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">Buy from a Trusted UK Registered Autograph &amp; Memorabilia Company</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p><img src="http://i99.photobucket.com/albums/l287/petecowgill/Banners2011/TopBanner.jpg" border="0" class="websiteignore" alt="Up North Memorabilia Ltd"></p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p><img src="http://i99.photobucket.com/albums/l287/petecowgill/MAY2014/4MAY445.jpg" border="0" alt="GENUINE HAND SIGNED AUTOGRAPH PHOTO FROM UP NORTH MEMORABILIA"></p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p><img src="http://i99.photobucket.com/albums/l287/petecowgill/MAY2014/4MAY446.jpg" border="0" alt="GENUINE HAND SIGNED AUTOGRAPH PHOTO FROM UP NORTH MEMORABILIA"></p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </div>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p class="headline">Item Description</p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</div><div class="tplContent" style="z-index:1; position:relative;"><span style="line-height: 1.4em;"><div class="showonwebsite">We have on offer an A4 Photo Display Hand Signed by Olympic Legend Dame Kelly Holmes.<span style="line-height: 1.4em;">&nbsp;The overall size of this piece is A4 (Just like a standard piece of A4 paper - approx 21x30cm) and comprises of a 6x4 Inch Photo and a 5x3 Inch Genuine Autographed card. We have tried to create a range that will suit Gift buyers and collectors alike. These are a great size to give as presents to Sons and Daughters, Brothers and Sisters, or cousins, nieces and nephews! Being only A4 in size it means these pieces will be popular Christmas/Birthday gifts that wont break the bank. Saying all that, these items are still&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 1.4em;">Unique</span><span style="line-height: 1.4em;">&nbsp;Pieces of Autographed Memorabilia - Fans and Collectors of any Age would love one of these in their Autograph Collection!&nbsp;We supply a Certificate of Authenticity &amp; Lifetime Guarantee with EVERY Item and also Offer FREE UK Postage on ALL orders. We have been selling Sports/Entertainment Memorabilia for more than 12 years so you can rest assured that what you receive will be 100% Genuine and&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 1.4em;">Guaranteed</span><span style="line-height: 1.4em;">.&nbsp;For further information on this or any other item please email us on:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:info@upnorthmemorabilia.com?Subject=Listing Question" style="line-height: 1.4em; text-align: center;">info@upnorthmemorabilia.com</a><br></div>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p class="headline">Trust in Us</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p>All Items sold by Up North Memorabilia Ltd are 100% Genuine &amp; Hand Signed. We do not sell Copies, Auto-Pens or Prints, everything you see is actually hand signed by the stated Player/Celeb/Star.</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p class="headline">Certificate Of Authenticity (COA)</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p>Every Item comes with what is known as a Certificate of Authenticity (COA)&nbsp;which&nbsp;is your assurance that what you purchase is 100% Genuine.</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p class="headline">100% Money Back Guarantee</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p>Customer satisfaction is our primary concern, if for any reason you are not totally happy with your item - simply return it to us for a Full refund. No Quibbles, No troubles and No questions asked.</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p class="headline">Payment &amp; Postage</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p>We accept all Major Credit/Debit cards - All payments are processed by PayPal - Please note that you do not need a Paypal account to shop with us - we can take payment from your Credit/Debit card, please contact us for more details. We aim to dispatch all orders the same day, for guaranteed same day dispatch please complete payment before 3pm. We also offer a next day guaranteed delivery, again please contact us for this. We Ship Internationally and will post Worldwide. Shipping rates are quoted above.</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p class="headline">Up North Memorabilia - About Us</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p>Established in 2003, Up North Memorabilia was born out of a university student who was&nbsp;fascinated&nbsp;with autographs and had been an avid&nbsp;collector&nbsp;since 1998. From day one that university student knew that Authenticity was Key to a successful &amp; enjoyable autograph collection. Over the next decade Up North Memorabilia went from strength to strength&nbsp;acquiring&nbsp;many, many contacts in the field and in time&nbsp;built up an unprecedented&nbsp;following.</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p>Today we hold the same strong values, every item we sell comes with both a Certificate of Authenticity &amp; a lifetime money back Guarantee. For peace of mind our company contact details are printed on the&nbsp;Certificates. Up North Memorabilia is a Limited company &amp; is registered at&nbsp;companies&nbsp;house, our registration number is 8057961. We are a full time registered autograph business, our Vat number is 126195417 and our contact details can be found at the bottom of this listing. We are based in the Manchester, North-West of England (UK).</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p>The vast majority of our Items are obtained by us, the few that are not are sourced from companies and collectors we have been dealing for several years and these companies have the same high standards as us, if they didn''t we simply wouldn''t deal with them. We attend very many signing sessions where sports stars (past &amp; present) are paid to sign items for us - we also have some unbelievably great contacts in the entertainment industry and a very many of the items that we obtain are signed especially for us. As is the nature of the Industry, autographs and signatures can vary ever so slightly - we may have more then one of a particular item, if so the item you will receive will be exactly as pictured, but the autograph maybe placed slightly differently. You will probably not notice this at all and the autograph on your item will be of the same high quality &amp; will of course be 100% Genuine &amp; Authentic. For more information on this please see <a href="http://stores.ebay.co.uk/Up-North-Memorabilia-and-Autographs/duplicates">here</a></p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p>Whenever possible we take photographs of the players/stars/celebs signing for us, for&nbsp;logistical&nbsp;reasons it is impossible to photograph every single item being signed. Showing that we were present and the celeb/star was signing for us is what we feel is most important, and we strongly&nbsp;believe&nbsp;it is the best way of showing you that your item is 100% genuine and hand signed. We have been trading for more than 12 years and know the Industry inside out, please rest assured that anything purchased from us is going to be 100% Genuine.</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p class="headline">Contact Us</p>
&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <p>If you have ANY questions at all please do get in touch with us, we are available 7 days a week. You can contact us via the ebay messages system or you can email us direct at&nbsp;<a href="mailto:info@upnorthmemorabilia.com?Subject=ebay" style="text-align: center;">info@upnorthmemorabilia.com</a></p>
