<P style="MARGIN: 0px 0px 11px; FONT: 14px Arial; COLOR: #101010"><FONT size=4>a&nbsp;Limited Edition Official Team GB&nbsp;signed 8x10"&nbsp;colour photograph that has been personally hand signed by Kelly Holmes.&nbsp;</FONT></P>
<P style="MARGIN: 0px 0px 11px; FONT: 14px Arial; COLOR: #101010"><FONT size=4>This photograph comes complete with a uniquely numbered hologram which you could&nbsp;register on the London 2012 official Sporting Memorabilia website. An official&nbsp;card giving details on how to register your authentic signed item online&nbsp;is also included.&nbsp;&nbsp;</FONT></P>
